      "sc:citation": {
        "@id": "https://doi.org/10.1101/2025.02.02.25321536"
      },
      "sc:description": "ImputeBench is an R package and vignette designed to benchmark single imputation methods for missing values. It provides a standardized, empirical approach to select imputation methods in the context of specific data problems, connecting to existing missing value imputation research and offering a reproducible implementation.",
